# Snipe-IT Automation Script

This automation script uses **.NET 8** and **Microsoft.Playwright** to interact with the Snipe-IT demo site.

##  Steps Automated

- Logs into [https://demo.snipeitapp.com](https://demo.snipeitapp.com)
- Creates a "Macbook Pro 13" asset
- Sets the status to **"Ready to Deploy"**
- Checks it out to a random user
- Verifies the asset is listed
- Confirms asset details
- Verifies asset creation and checkout in the history tab

##  Tech Stack

- .NET 8
- Playwright for .NET

##  How to Run

1. Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/snipeit-automation.git
cd snipeit-automation
2.Install dependencies:
dotnet restore
3.Install Playwright browsers:
playwright install
4.Run the test:
dotnet test



